projects.title: Build a website for an online wellbeing program
projects.description:
We have a program that helps people manage their wellbeing. It's paper based and we want to take it online. We need an online website / web platform that is secure and used these technologies:
HTML, CSS, jQuery, JavaScript, AJAX
PHP Laravel
MySQL
Linux
We want it hosted in Australia, and a total quote for the build, design, testing, and support and any bug fixing for 1 year. 
As a basis, user must be able to log in do basic wellbeing assessments (e.g. "how happy are you on a scale of 0 to 10), and input information into their dashboard (e.g., i define wellbeing as X) - and (my wellbeing plan is X). The dashboard will also host various wellbeing activities in video format and pdf format. 
At a higher level, a manager should be able to log into and monitor various users progress and dashboards. 
At a super user level, the super user should be able to enroll multiple accounts. 
The build is also needed to be completed within 2 months from start to finish, with an ongoing discount applied if not completed on time. 
We are after experienced developers only, so much have a proven track record of this kind of development.

projects.title: Desarrollar un sitio web
projects.description:
Es un proceso de matrículas para un colegio en el cual los padres deben hacer 5 pasos:
Ingresar con usuario único.
Registrar el hijo o hijos (uno a uno)
Descargar los precios que el colegio ya asigno a ese padre.
Descargar el contrato ya pre diligenciado para la firma
Descargar manual de convivencia para firmar.
Descargar instrucciones adicionales.
Todo debe estar pre diligenciado con los datos exactos del padre que ingreso y el niño al que se refiere.
Luego los padres ingresan todo los documentos en archivos de PDF y envían y el sistema notifica a los administradores que el proceso ya fue realizado.

El sistema tiene tres tipos de roles o jerarquías.
Super admin.
Admin.
Padres.
